# Eval outputs.
#
# The generated markdown reports (results/results.md, results/scale_curve.md,
# results/audit.md) are the PUBLISHED RECORD of a run and stay tracked, along
# with the hand-written results/clean_clone.md. Raw Inspect logs and
# per-episode transcripts are large and regenerable (scripts/run_evals.py) —
# ignore those.
results/logs/
results/transcripts/

# Alternate run output dirs, e.g. scripts/smoke_eval.sh --out results-smoke.
results-*/

# Agent tooling scratch worktrees.
